    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i dont really want to go to the clinic if i dont have to, it's always so expensive and the wait is crazy. it doesnt feel like it's broken or anything, just really bruised and puffy. if i just keep it elevated and ice it every hour, it'll probably be fine in like 3 or 4 days right?",
