    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what exactly is the risk? i mean, it's just an ankle. if it's just a strain, won't it just heal on its own as long as i stay off it? i really feel like i can manage this at home with some ibuprofen and ice. surely it's not worth a whole doctor visit just for some swelling.",
